features: 【OPTIMAL EYE PROTECTION】Eye Protection newest indoor protective glasses designed for working under various hydroponic grow lights – Green lenses designed for use under LED lighting systems. Color Correction These glasses were specifically designed to see your indoor LED garden as it would appear outside in natural daylight. Protect Health Blocks all UVA and UVB rays and protects your eyes from infrared wavelengths, glare and reflection.

【UV BLOCKING】: Perfect uv 400 Pro lens against uv-a uv-b uv-c and IR, and protects your eyes from infrared wavelengths, glare and reflection. Reduce eyestrain and alleviate the pain from harsh lighting
【COLOR CORRECTION】: Green lenses correct red and blue color emitted by LED grow lights. Close to natural color correction can enhance more details under red-violet grow light environment
【HEALTH BENEFITS】: Effectively reduces eyestrain, headache, fatigue and dizziness while working under extremely bright grow lights

【LIGHTWEIGHT & SAFETY】: Super lightweight design gives your hours of long-wear comfort while working in your grow room, grow tent, greenhouse or growing space. Impact resistant and scratch proof polycarbonate material protects front and side of your eyes completely.
